cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper deals with object recognition, specifically the challenge of detecting small objects, in this case, small faces. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning and multi-task learning, which are common topics in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of templates and receptive fields, which are topics in cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
